description: Luce Douady was seen as a future star of the climbing world after wowing in senior competition.
title: Luce Douady: French 16-year-old climber dies from fall
title_page: Luce Douady: French 16-year-old climber dies from fall - BBC News
maintext: Bouldering requires competitors to try to climb fixed routes within a time limit. It is one of the disciplines when sports climbing makes its debut at next year's rescheduled Tokyo Olympics.
